race.description: Apg Yearling Sales 2YOF Final Mobile Pace (G2)
race.comment: The marble has fallen nicely for PRE EMINANT (3) who was good from the back row last week, racing wide before working to the front and sticking on for second. Had won three in a row prior and should get her chance from this draw. Stablemate ARRHYTHMIA (8) came from wide on the second line to beat PRE EMINANT last week, stretching her undefeated run to six. Draws on the second line again so may be relying on a little luck but but it is impossible to knock what she has been doing. The same could be said for STAR TO FALL (9) who draws on the back row but has come from there to win in both rounds of the series so far, taking her overall record to four from five. CONCILIATE (4) is a consistent filly who placed from this barrier last week and looks a first four hope again as does HILLTOP BLOSSOM (1) who won the last time she drew on the pegs.
